CHANGELOG


v0.8.0
------

- generalized login url (sso or ldap or local by settings)
- saml2 configuration (on top of djangosaml2)
- Unical agid template
- logging enabled with detailed logs
- ldap json dumps on each user login
- better unit tests
- localization improved
- dashboard with a new messages regarding invalid identities
- users can change their username only a time!
- username blacklists (on db)
